  "3096320": {
    "name": "Death and Tactics",
    "steam_appid": 3096320,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096320/extras/7fdc31ec68d160e84bfe920eab0c41d0.avif?t=1772239039\" width=620 height=123 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>&quot;Death and Tactics&quot;<strong> </strong></i>is a top-down Strategy RPG inspired by <i>&quot;Lisa: The Painful&quot;</i> and the <i>&quot;Fire Emblem&quot; </i>series with a heavy focus on permanent death elements.  With 51 playable characters, each with their own unique items to unlock and events to experience depending on on who lives and who dies in your party, <i>&quot;Death and Tactics&quot;</i> is an incredibly replayable experience where your choices in the gameplay have long lasting consequences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One of the overall goals is to be a Strategy RPG that doesn't waste your time. Permanent death is incorporated into almost every system to create convenience. Players won't ever feel pressured to do something like restart a level if one of their party members falls in battle. Each death or mistake creates a new strategic opportunity for the player to explore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096320/extras/5e463610b583feb7e781de632b26517d.avif?t=1772239039\" width=620 height=123 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 years after nuclear bombs wiped out most of humanity, mutants wander the earth and the last remnants of humanity are divided. While some leaders decided to take a more &quot;old-school&quot; approach to governance...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096320/extras/3442ae9e3d3b283a78906190dca25c50.avif?t=1772239039\" width=127 height=163 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Others have had... more unique ideas on how to take advantage of the apocalypse to, say the least...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096320/extras/5145ded058d929532d61028ee9c6d441.webp?t=1772239039\" width=228 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During the events of the story, you play as Tanya, a young woman in her 20s, an aspiring playwright, and owner of a mutated horse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096320/extras/dad06d72f72fd26180ad6800005e42ff.webp?t=1772239039\" width=49 height=49 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, her happy-go-lucky life is soon interrupted by the cruel realities that come with trying to survive in the apocalypse. Join her and her friends as they undergo a journey of loss, vengeance, and growth across this ruined world and interact with the freaks that inhabit it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096320/extras/7a2bcf51064afd08e52fc96c435b2246.avif?t=1772239039\" width=620 height=123 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-50 playable characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096320/extras/b632ce8266707e84a2b500c015a06885.webp?t=1772239039\" width=228 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-The &quot;Rage&quot; system, which powers up your party members if their loved ones fall in battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096320/extras/2286c97b6eb115dc7c9b6de1c4a0f93e.webp?t=1772239039\" width=96 height=25 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Selling the organs of the party members you don't like for money.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096320/extras/df02b4fccaf7485cbe28029608c53e60.avif?t=1772239039\" width=150 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-A &quot;well meaning&quot; weapons manufacturer that will frequently offer you new and unique weapons to spice up your strategies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096320/extras/9d975c9b49e61609070292bf03467451.avif?t=1772239039\" width=150 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-A pair of personal fitness trainers to level up any of your party members if they've fallen behind, ensuring that all 50 characters are usable throughout the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096320/extras/66da5b1b0631e7219a8f516af781e1da.avif?t=1772239039\" width=300 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Alternative events with unlockable items and skills depending on how you've played the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096320/extras/86e7481ffa3496f459cf48b461adff02.avif?t=1772239039\" width=865 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Over 100 skills. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096320/extras/91517a30de695febc7cc33ebb67ca546.webp?t=1772239039\" width=192 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-A deep strategic experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096320/extras/d0535bb8490f7316e0006650032498f0.avif?t=1772239039\" width=351 height=306 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096320/extras/5ea31333942859b7c55b433a111b7273.avif?t=1772239039\" width=620 height=123 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you would like to keep up with official updates of the game on social media, our official accounts can be found here on twitter at &quot;@DeathAndTactics&quot; and on Bluesky at &quot;@deathandtactics.bsky.social&quot;.</p>",
